repository.name: RPHAX
repository.description: RPHAX provides a quick automation flow to develop and prototype hardware accelerators on Xilinx FPGAs. Currently, the framework has support for AXI-Stream IP with Single Master and Single Slave Template. The user can code the Hardware Accelerator in TL-Verilog/Verilog/System Verilog and use this flow to automatically package into an IP and create a Zynq based block design.
